Brilliant in every aspect, this large contemporary residence offers an idyllic family-focused lifestyle of quality and space within easy walking distance to Keilor Village. Description:
FABULOUS FAMILY LIFESTYLE – INSIDE AND OUT
Contemporary living at its best, this beautifully renovated residence offers an impressive indoor/outdoor lifestyle perfect for families that love to entertain! Located in a quiet cul-de-sac, the home features a highly versatile interior comprising three large upstairs bedrooms (two with BIRs, master with WIR and designer shoe-room), luxury ensuite and main bathroom. Downstairs: big study/fourth bedroom, spacious lounge complete with bar, open living/dining areas and large modern kitchen with all-Blanco cooking appliances and dishwasher, guest powder room. Extensive features include ducted heating and multiple split-system a/c, plantation shutters and polished hardwood floors, internally accessed tandem double garage. Step out to a sensational entertainers’ backyard featuring expansive paved area with weatherproof cantilever umbrella, deck/pergola, 5-seater spa – all surrounded by lush fully-landscaped gardens. A terrific home in a family-focused neighbourhood, it’s close to local schools and public transport, freeway access, parkland, Keilor Village shops and cafés. Land approx 623sqm.
Agents; Nelson Alexander Pty Ltd

Description:
Stylish, Private and Secure living all in one
Upon entering this elevated stylish rendered family home you are overwhelmed with charm and character this property has to offer. With two living areas catering for the most discerning of buyers, this property ticks all boxes. The open plan living combines a lounge/ living and dining area all highlighted by the warmth of polished floor boards, high ornate ceiling and soft tone colours. The kitchen is finished with Caesar Stone bench and ample vinyl wrap cupboards which would make any Chef envious. The property boasts 4 generous size bedrooms plus a study or 5th bedroom. The master has a superb ensuite and walk thru robe. The second bedroom has its own ensuite and would suit a growing teenager, stay over guests or even the mother in law. At the rear of the property we have the rumpus/theatre room finished with PFB, which steps out to a majestic decked area that has LETS PARTY written all over it. Lets not forget the 2 car garage with internal access. All this, within walking distance to the beautiful Keilor Village.

Description:
KEILOR VILLAGE BECKONS
Get the best of both worlds with this extensive three bedroom plus study family home offering a country inspired locale, and nearby city conveniences. Around the corner from lively Keilor Village, scenic Brimbank Park, schools, great sporting facilities and easy freeway access this tasteful family home offers dual living zones, alfresco entertaining and modern appointments. Huge formal lounge and dining room with two bay windows. Gleaming kitchen and large meals area adjoins the sizeable family room and outdoor covered entertaining area with atrium roof. Separate study, three double bedrooms, master with ensuite, main bathroom, ducted heating, rev/cycle heating and cooling plus a double garage. Give your family a hint of country, while still retaining all the benefits of city life.

Description:
A LANDMARK RESIDENCE OF UNRIVALLED LUXURY
In Keilor’s premier location, this expansive home on approximately half an acre showcases the very best in modern style and uncompromised attention to detail offering its occupants an exclusive and ultimately rewarding lifestyle experience. Impressive yet warmly inviting, the stunning interior features four double bedrooms (three with BIRs, master with WIR), luxurious ensuite and main bathroom, big home office or fifth bedroom, Smeg/Bosch equipped kitchen with striking quartz benchtops and large breakfast bar, spacious formal lounge and dining areas (vaulted ceilings) plus big rumpus/living, family-sized laundry and internal access into the double garage/workshop (remote). Extensive highlights include ducted heating and evaporative cooling throughout, Heat ‘n’ Glo fireplace (lounge), ducted vacuum and alarm systems, superb Grey Ironbark floors, finest quality fittings, electric security shutters, UPS (uninterrupted power supply) and much more. Step outside to an enormous north-facing backyard with massive undercover entertaining area and fully automated solar-heated pool. This amazing home delivers a lifestyle without compare – perfectly positioned in the area’s most enviable neighbourhood.
Agents: Nelson Alexander Pty Ltd
